## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full complexity of interactions in all industries. Additionally, the rapid pace of technological change means that the dynamics of these interactions are continually evolving, potentially outdating some insights. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these relationships across different sectors and regions.